===Etymology===
Originally meant [[arrowhead]], or the [[barb]]([[point]]) of an [[arrow]]. Also meant [[flat]] [[arrowhead]]. Later its meaning collapsed to the meaning of 'to give' from {{lang|zh|畀予}}. Also see {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*s-bəj-n/k||to give}}. Cognate with {{cog|bo|སྦྱིན||to give, to bestow}} and {{cog|my|ပေး||to give}}.

